<p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 36px; background-color: rgb(227, 239, 208);">本次检查既侧重于宿舍卫生以及用电安全两方面，更在于向同学们强调及强化安全意识，打造文明宿舍。活动在检查寝室卫生情况时，主要集中于地面、墙面、门窗玻璃的洁净，个人用品、公共设施等物品摆放是否整齐，寝室有无异味，阳台、卫生间有无杂物，床上用品是否摆放整洁，门口物品是否整齐等。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 36px; background-color: rgb(227, 239, 208);"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEIvUBKKARI1TklSzfB1tafFWbCJUgFwtRWHyBdN8NVMe5k9cSwia0RufXFqKIjicHXWWIjia5EFk6fkg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="250" height="154" style="width: 250px; height: 154px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(227, 239, 208); text-indent: 2.25em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">在查寝过程中，辅导员与学生们亲切交流，了解学生的住宿情况，并提醒同学们注意自己的人身财产安全，要预防电信诈骗等，提高警惕性。学生会成员们认真负责，亲切有礼，温馨提醒学生杜绝使用违规电器，保证用电安全，同时对同学们的日常生活和学习情况进行了解，整个检查过程进行得很顺利，同学们都积极配合。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(227, 239, 208); text-indent: 2.25em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">从检查结果来看，大部分宿舍总体干净整洁，桌面上物品及其他生活用品摆放整齐，并未发现违规电器。</span></p><p><br/></p>